    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that doesn't need to be a showpiece. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain spots. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few stains, though it remains functional and comfortable. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and suspension work in the near future to keep it at its best. It's a dependable car with plenty of life left, provided the new owner is comfortable with its cosmetic imperfections and minor mechanical needs.",
      "price": 21500.0,
