    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence, this vehicle has been maintained to a high standard of care. It offers a seamless integration of performance and sophisticated styling, ensuring a commanding presence on the road. Meticulously inspected to confirm its mechanical reliability and structural integrity, this unit represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a balance of value and superior quality.",
      "price": 36500.0,
